
<style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body, html {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .hero {
      background: url('../assets/Purple-and-Pink-Pastel-Simple-Modern-Payment-Mobile-App-Presentation-1.gif') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 5%;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    .fondo {
      background: url('../assets/Hulux_(1).gif') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 30%;
      background-attachment: fixed; 
    }

    .content {
      color: white;
      max-width: 1200px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #ff5722;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn1 {
      background-color: #ff5722;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 2px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #15294f;
    }
    .btn1:hover {
      background-color: #15294f;
    }

    /* ✅ Sección azul */
    .info-section {
      background-color: #11293e; 
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 5px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .info-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;

    }

    .info-section p {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      max-width: 1500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    


    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .info-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .info-section p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .btn {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero con imagen de fondo -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>El Internet más confiable y además veloz.</h1>
      <p>Conectamos con las cosas que importan, impulsando experiencias confiables y de alta velocidad.</p>
      <a href="/servicios" class="btn">Ver más</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

